    <h2>Beaches</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>Enjoy white sand beaches around Yellow Leaf Bay or explore secluded rocky coastlines ideal for snorkeling and sunbathing.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="rainforest">
    <h2>Rainforest</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>Take a guided zip-lining adventure or a self-paced hike through Taniti’s lush rainforest trails filled with native wildlife and waterfalls.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="volcano">
    <h2>Volcano</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>Tour Taniti’s small active volcano with expert guides and enjoy panoramic views of the island’s interior.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="sightseeing">
    <h2>Sightseeing</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>Take island bus or boat tours, visit Merriton Landing, and explore Taniti City’s architecture and museums.</p>
    </div>
